attributes.review: As soon as I download the app, it starts to make my phone super glitchy, I thought it could be another cause, so I looked passed it. As soon as I open the app it started asking me for too much info, just me to just sign in, like bruh 🤨. cmon now........ Tonald Drump think he slick or sumn tryna get all my info, as if I’m not already in a gov. database but anyways, when I deleted this horrible app, my phone BLACKED OUT. I couldn’t turn it on or gain any interaction with my phone for MINUTES BRUH. during that time my phone’s speakers were blasting a speech from a Tonald Drump rally and I was bout to cry real tears.His voice is so agonizing, I had to leave my house and get some fresh air. I stepped into my car and drove to a chipotle. I got a fire bowl and it was good ash. as soon as I got home, pulling in the driveway my heart went:”DUMDUM, DUMDUM” cuz i remembered the voice of Tonald and I got scared. I crept back in the crib and my phone seemed back to normal,  I guess someone has my personal info like my iCloud stuff and the secret Krabby patty formula I got when I blackmailed plankton cuz he was cheating on Karen with S- you know what, 👁......👁 I spoke to much, back on track. BUT THEN SUDDENLY TONALDS VOICE COMES BACK LOUDER THAN EVER, MY PHONE SCREEN (INTERNALLY) LOOKS LIKE I BEAT IT UP ON A CURB and then my stomach starts to turn because if the horrific sound of our Presidents speech.i couldn’t take it anymore, neither did my bowel movements, I rushed to the bathroom. and......the rest......was history.......
